snippet.title: Gods Unchained - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gods Unchained is a decentralized competitive card game that takes some of the best lessons learned from games like Hearthstone, MTG, and Faeria and turns them into a truly community-focused game. Website: https://godsunchained.com/

At its core Gods Unchained is a state of the art blockchain-based game, enabling users to trade and sell their cards freely, with the same level of ownership as if they were real, tangible cards.

Note: This is original announcement game board which has now been updated.
